SDScoreBoard
------------

This is a sample project illustrating some basic Core Animation techniques, more information can be found at http://tr.im/v9mY. The source is commented to the extreme as this was produced as a teaching aid/sample project.

This code is released under the terms of the MIT license, more details can be found in the LICENSE file. Attribution back to http://daveverwer.com is appreciated, but not necessary. I would love to hear from anyone who ends up using this.